## ğŸ¯ Overview

**Airguard** is a complete IoT sensor data collection and monitoring system that combines:

- **ESP32-S3 Hardware**: Two devices communicating via ESP-NOW wireless protocol
- **Sensors**: GPS (NEO-6M), IMU (MPU6050), Temperature
- **Host Services**: Python gateway, MQTT broker, Node.js backend, MongoDB database
- **Real-time Dashboard**: WebSocket-powered web interface

### âœ¨ Key Features

âœ… **Wireless Data Collection** - ESP-NOW protocol (no WiFi router needed)  
âœ… **Multi-Sensor Support** - GPS, Accelerometer, Gyroscope, Temperature  
âœ… **Real-time Updates** - WebSocket streaming to browser dashboard  
âœ… **Local & Cloud Storage** - SQLite + MongoDB dual database  
âœ… **Production Ready** - Systemd services, health checks, monitoring  
âœ… **Easy Deployment** - One-command startup script  

